
To run the code living in SingleTop-tW:
(Fall11 release)


cvs co -r CMSSW_42X -d TopBrussels UserCode/TopBrusselscd TopBrussels/TopTreeProducer
scramv1 b
cd src
make -j 8
cd ../../TopTreeAnalysis
make all
make btag
cp SingleTop-tW/maketW .


mkdir SingleTop-tW/outputs
cd SingleTop-tW/scripts
ln -s ../outputs/ outputs

mkdir results
cd -


sh maketW tWTMVA

cd SingleTop-tW/


modify the .xml files to the right paths of the files, and that's it:

./tWTMVA.exe --emu

(everything should run directly)

